high_descs: walk forwards to the kitchen sink on the right
grab the egg out of the left side kitchen sink
turn around and walk over to the fridge on the right side
place the egg inside of the fridge, let it cool, then take it back out
turn right and walk back over to the kitchen sink ahead
place the egg inside of the microwave above the kitchen sink
anns.task_desc: place a cooled egg inside the microwave

high_descs: Go forward to the counter, then turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the egg from in the sink.
Turn around and move forward, then turn right to face the fridge.
Chill the egg inside of the fridge.
Turn around, then turn left and return to the sink, then look up to the microwave above it.
Put the egg in the microwave, then close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold egg in the microwave.

high_descs: Move forward two steps and turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the egg from the left side of the sink.
Hold the egg and turn around. Turn right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the egg inside. Shut the door and then open the door. Take out the egg and shut the door.
Carry the egg and turn to the right to face the sink.
Place the egg above the sink in the microwave and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Chill an egg and place it in the microwave.
